entries.femaleVariant: You really saved my ass. I can't thank you enough.
They'll be looking for you.
What now? You're gonna sell this ride?
Wouldn't stick around too long if I were you.
What about the ride? You gonna fence it?
6th Street're gonna be searchin' high an' low for this beauty.
I'm leavin' town today.
It's like Uncle Estevez always said – "If you gotta choose between your ride and savin' someone else's ass, always choose the ride."
Least you know that a ride's never gonna betray you. People, on the other hand...
I have to sooner or later. Know a guy in Sacramento – a collector. He'll set me up for life.
But for now, I'm takin' 'er with me, spruce her up a little more.
Ain't no one that can't be replaced, huh? I'm curious to know how the fuck you'll replace Jake. Go on, humor me.
Nature doesn't leave empty spaces. Someone'll turn up.
Only empty space the one's inside your skull.
The soft, the calibrations, even the go-betweens for the tech were his!
We'll be drinking shit through straws – tell you that much.
He said this baby's untraceable. Whole thing's basically swapped out, part for part.
Fucking Estevez. And he locked everything down?
Serial's scrubbed off, soft's packed with ICE, everything inside's a lost cause. I mean, I don't even know where to start...
You're lookin' at a masterpiece of auto-tuning.
Pff. Yeah...
